WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.190
Good morning, family. How are you all

00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:05.230
doing today? Praise the Lord. I had a

00:00:05.240 --> 00:00:08.110
dream last night, and the Lord spoke to

00:00:08.120 --> 00:00:11.830
me, warning me to

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:14.230
warn you all about watching your

00:00:14.240 --> 00:00:16.269
children during the holiday season. When

00:00:16.279 --> 00:00:19.189
you're going out shopping, don't get

00:00:19.199 --> 00:00:22.830
distracted. If you take

00:00:22.840 --> 00:00:26.029
them into a mall or a major

00:00:26.039 --> 00:00:29.070
retail store, don't get distracted with

00:00:29.080 --> 00:00:30.870
your surroundings.

00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:32.910
I saw that there was a

00:00:32.920 --> 00:00:37.110
plan while people were distracted;

00:00:37.120 --> 00:00:39.030
they had children

00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:40.670
wandering around, going off from

00:00:40.680 --> 00:00:43.389
them a little bit to

00:00:43.389 --> 00:00:43.399
look at

00:00:43.399 --> 00:00:45.950
presents or something from the

00:00:45.960 --> 00:00:49.910
store. These were younger kids, probably

00:00:49.910 --> 00:00:49.920
ten

00:00:49.920 --> 00:00:54.549
years old and younger. I saw

00:00:54.559 --> 00:00:57.509
men watching the

00:00:57.519 --> 00:01:00.509
children and watching the parents

00:01:00.519 --> 00:01:02.590
secretly, as

00:01:02.590 --> 00:01:02.600
if

00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:04.469
they didn't know

00:01:04.479 --> 00:01:06.590
they were being followed. These

00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:10.270
mothers were distracted with all the

00:01:10.280 --> 00:01:12.510
other kids. If you had

00:01:12.520 --> 00:01:14.950
two or three kids with

00:01:14.960 --> 00:01:17.109
you, you would be distracted with

00:01:17.119 --> 00:01:19.030
shopping because the

00:01:19.040 --> 00:01:21.710
places were full of people. As the

00:01:21.720 --> 00:01:23.590
other kid would wander off,

00:01:23.600 --> 00:01:27.069
I saw the men

00:01:27.079 --> 00:01:29.429
assigned to grab these children

00:01:29.429 --> 00:01:29.439
for

00:01:29.439 --> 00:01:32.310
bad

00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:34.230
intentions. This

00:01:34.230 --> 00:01:34.240
is

00:01:34.240 --> 00:01:36.950
something we can

00:01:36.960 --> 00:01:39.550
pray against today. I've seen in

00:01:39.560 --> 00:01:42.910
the comments where people ask, "Where did the 350,000 kids go?"After my son

00:01:50.640 --> 00:01:52.990
brought that up, I had this

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:55.069
dream. I know when the Lord's

00:01:55.079 --> 00:01:56.749
speaking to me because I wake up and

00:01:56.759 --> 00:01:58.270
can't stop thinking about it all day;

00:01:58.280 --> 00:02:00.029
it's stirring in my spirit.

00:02:00.039 --> 00:02:01.469
I believe the Lord

00:02:01.479 --> 00:02:05.310
is warning me to warn you all so

00:02:05.320 --> 00:02:08.430
that you are on

00:02:08.440 --> 00:02:11.470
guard. I've

00:02:11.480 --> 00:02:13.470
warned you about being in public places

00:02:13.480 --> 00:02:15.710
already because of people doing stupid

00:02:15.720 --> 00:02:21.229
things with mass shootings and big events. I am

00:02:21.229 --> 00:02:21.239
praying over

00:02:21.239 --> 00:02:23.190
the Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade

00:02:23.200 --> 00:02:25.869
next week,

00:02:25.869 --> 00:02:25.879
Rockin'New

00:02:25.879 --> 00:02:29.390
Year's Eve,

00:02:29.390 --> 00:02:29.400
Atlanta—because

00:02:29.400 --> 00:02:31.949
He showed

00:02:31.959 --> 00:02:33.229
me Atlanta—the shopping

00:02:33.239 --> 00:02:35.309
malls, and events in

00:02:35.319 --> 00:02:37.390
general because it's a very active

00:02:37.400 --> 00:02:39.550
time of year. This was just another

00:02:39.560 --> 00:02:41.430
thing the Lord brought up to

00:02:41.440 --> 00:02:44.949
tell people: watch your

00:02:44.959 --> 00:02:48.430
children. Do not walk in fear; it's not a

00:02:48.440 --> 00:02:50.350
call to fear, but a call to

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:54.270
prayer so that your

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:56.309
antenna is up.

00:02:56.319 --> 00:02:58.630
Keep your antennas up

00:02:58.640 --> 00:03:00.470
because the enemy

00:03:00.480 --> 00:03:02.350
has a plan all the time to kill, steal,

00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:05.589
and destroy. We pray against those

00:03:05.599 --> 00:03:07.949
plans so that people are watching their

00:03:07.959 --> 00:03:11.949
kids and their surroundings

00:03:11.959 --> 00:03:14.350
when they go shopping. It's an exciting

00:03:14.360 --> 00:03:16.270
time, and people are not paying

00:03:16.280 --> 00:03:18.030
attention because they

00:03:18.030 --> 00:03:18.040
are looking

00:03:18.040 --> 00:03:20.910
at sales.

00:03:20.910 --> 00:03:20.920
I

00:03:20.920 --> 00:03:24.270
wanted to

00:03:24.280 --> 00:03:27.030
shed some light on

00:03:27.040 --> 00:03:31.110
an enemy plan to

00:03:31.120 --> 00:03:33.710
kidnap children and take them into

00:03:33.720 --> 00:03:35.710
slavery. I've been praying

00:03:35.720 --> 00:03:38.509
over the war,

00:03:38.519 --> 00:03:42.270
interceding for what I believe

00:03:42.280 --> 00:03:46.030
would be an acceleration of what I've

00:03:46.040 --> 00:03:48.149
seen

00:03:48.159 --> 00:03:50.710
coming. I believe the Lord wants to give

00:03:50.720 --> 00:03:52.550
us a

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:57.550
window of extended grace and

00:03:57.560 --> 00:03:59.949
favor, turning things around with the

00:03:59.959 --> 00:04:01.910
economy. I've told you all

00:04:01.910 --> 00:04:01.920
about

00:04:01.920 --> 00:04:03.750
the attack against the economy

00:04:03.750 --> 00:04:03.760
and

00:04:03.760 --> 00:04:05.509
the house of

00:04:05.519 --> 00:04:07.509
cards

00:04:07.519 --> 00:04:08.710
falling.

00:04:08.720 --> 00:04:11.710
My son

00:04:11.720 --> 00:04:12.990
is

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:16.629
making a video for you right

00:04:16.639 --> 00:04:20.030
now, and this was the Antichrist flag

00:04:20.040 --> 00:04:22.670
that the Lord showed me when I went to

00:04:22.680 --> 00:04:25.230
tribulation with Jesus. This is what the

00:04:25.240 --> 00:04:28.749
Antichrist will raise up and put on

00:04:28.759 --> 00:04:31.909
all the buildings whenever he is ruling.

00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:36.710
He makes you take down your country's flag

00:04:36.710 --> 00:04:36.720
and

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:39.270
put up his.

00:04:44.120 --> 00:04:46.469
I tried

00:04:46.479 --> 00:04:49.189
to the best of

00:04:49.199 --> 00:04:52.350
my ability to remember the

00:04:52.350 --> 00:04:52.360
five stars representing

00:04:52.360 --> 00:04:54.270
the five pillars of Islam.

00:04:56.919 --> 00:05:03.029
It

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.270
is

00:05:11.120 --> 00:05:13.270
very interesting, like the UN logo, but this is the

00:05:13.280 --> 00:05:17.830
old Afghan flag from

00:05:17.840 --> 00:05:20.029
the

00:05:20.039 --> 00:05:22.629
2000s.

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:26.430
After

00:05:26.440 --> 00:05:28.029
Afghanistan fell, it was the Northern

00:05:28.039 --> 00:05:29.830
Alliance flag

00:05:29.830 --> 00:05:29.840
that

00:05:29.840 --> 00:05:32.309
this

00:05:32.319 --> 00:05:35.510
actually looks like.

00:05:43.880 --> 00:05:46.830
My son made this, and it

00:05:46.840 --> 00:05:48.749
came right out of my spirit.

00:05:48.749 --> 00:05:48.759
When

00:05:48.759 --> 00:05:50.110
somebody said it

00:05:50.110 --> 00:05:50.120
looked

00:05:50.120 --> 00:05:52.749
like the Northern Afghanistan Alliance

00:05:52.759 --> 00:05:56.230
flag, I was like,

00:05:56.230 --> 00:05:56.240
"What?"I

00:05:56.240 --> 00:05:57.870
bring all this

00:05:57.880 --> 00:06:00.309
up

00:06:00.309 --> 00:06:00.319
to

00:06:00.319 --> 00:06:02.390
rehash it because

00:06:02.390 --> 00:06:02.400
there are

00:06:02.400 --> 00:06:04.990
a lot of new faces

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:08.909
here.

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:14.670
I'm grateful for every single one of

00:06:14.680 --> 00:06:16.430
you subscribing.

00:06:23.520 --> 00:06:27.189
I

00:06:27.199 --> 00:06:28.710
was out in the garage praying,

00:06:28.720 --> 00:06:30.309
and I heard the Lord tell me,

00:06:30.319 --> 00:06:36.070
"Trump will be known as a wartime

00:06:36.070 --> 00:06:36.080
president."I

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:39.790
thought, "Well, that's not good."I

00:06:39.790 --> 00:06:39.800
asked the

00:06:39.800 --> 00:06:43.510
Lord

00:06:43.510 --> 00:06:43.520
for

00:06:43.520 --> 00:06:48.230
the

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:50.350
direction

00:06:50.350 --> 00:06:50.360
of

00:06:50.360 --> 00:06:54.510
2025.

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:59.230
Are we going to

00:06:59.240 --> 00:07:02.950
have a major crash

00:07:02.950 --> 00:07:02.960
or

00:07:02.960 --> 00:07:06.070
see the house of cards

00:07:06.080 --> 00:07:09.029
fall? I was praying over the

00:07:09.039 --> 00:07:11.510
plague I've seen coming,

00:07:11.520 --> 00:07:14.589
the economy, and

00:07:14.599 --> 00:07:18.670
the new digital platform

00:07:18.680 --> 00:07:21.150
they're birthing.

00:07:21.160 --> 00:07:24.390
The

00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:28.070
Lord showed me key people in NATO

00:07:28.080 --> 00:07:32.589
were trying to stir up this war because

00:07:32.599 --> 00:07:34.510
Trump was going to try to pull out

00:07:34.520 --> 00:07:38.469
completely and not fund

00:07:38.479 --> 00:07:42.469
the Ukrainian thing. The Lord

00:07:42.469 --> 00:07:42.479
showed me

00:07:42.479 --> 00:07:44.350
Trump would

00:07:44.360 --> 00:07:47.110
try to strong-arm Putin, but the

00:07:47.120 --> 00:07:49.710
Lord said, "You will not be able to

00:07:49.720 --> 00:07:52.110
strong-arm Putin this way."He'll have to

00:07:52.120 --> 00:07:56.350
handle him with caution because

00:07:56.360 --> 00:08:00.589
things have escalated rapidly.

00:08:02.919 --> 00:08:05.990
We have to pray he has supernatural

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:10.350
wisdom on how to walk around landmines

00:08:13.720 --> 00:08:15.029
because you're dealing with an

00:08:15.039 --> 00:08:19.110
aggressive enemy that is like a

00:08:19.110 --> 00:08:19.120
wounded

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:21.790
animal.

00:08:21.800 --> 00:08:24.390
This

00:08:24.400 --> 00:08:26.830
war

00:08:26.830 --> 00:08:26.840
has

00:08:26.840 --> 00:08:29.670
been going on for four years. Emmanuel

00:08:29.670 --> 00:08:29.680
Macron

00:08:29.680 --> 00:08:35.029
has

00:08:35.029 --> 00:08:35.039
been

00:08:35.039 --> 00:08:38.310
kind of

00:08:38.320 --> 00:08:40.709
quiet since

00:08:40.719 --> 00:08:42.550
President Trump was announced,

00:08:42.560 --> 00:08:44.870
but

00:08:44.880 --> 00:08:47.870
I told you the UK would

00:08:47.880 --> 00:08:50.949
be involved, supplying

00:08:50.959 --> 00:08:52.750
missiles and

00:08:52.760 --> 00:08:56.470
trying to provoke a major World War

00:08:56.470 --> 00:08:56.480
III

00:08:56.480 --> 00:08:58.750
by sending these long-range weapons.

00:08:58.760 --> 00:09:02.110
Biden is going alongside it,

00:09:02.110 --> 00:09:02.120
saying

00:09:02.120 --> 00:09:03.430
they're

00:09:03.440 --> 00:09:05.630
innocent while giving

00:09:05.640 --> 00:09:07.550
these weapons. They're

00:09:07.560 --> 00:09:09.110
saying if you do this, we're going to use

00:09:09.120 --> 00:09:11.590
weapons we've never used

00:09:15.959 --> 00:09:19.110
before—weapons

00:09:24.079 --> 00:09:27.670
of mass

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:30.990
destruction,

00:09:33.519 --> 00:09:37.269
major

00:09:37.279 --> 00:09:40.269
artillery.

00:09:53.399 --> 00:09:57.269
Old Cold War alliances are trying to

00:09:57.279 --> 00:10:01.069
stir up again.

00:10:01.079 --> 00:10:03.230
The Lord showed me

00:10:03.240 --> 00:10:04.949
they would try to bring down the

00:10:04.959 --> 00:10:07.790
dollar through BRICS and other things.

00:10:07.800 --> 00:10:10.509
They were watching to see how

00:10:10.519 --> 00:10:13.389
President Trump or Kamala Harris

00:10:13.399 --> 00:10:16.590
would handle the

00:10:16.600 --> 00:10:19.590
next phases

00:10:19.600 --> 00:10:22.470
because they had a plan both

00:10:22.480 --> 00:10:24.829
ways. I believe it's through an

00:10:24.839 --> 00:10:26.710
acceleration of

00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:30.190
war.

00:10:30.200 --> 00:10:32.870
The

00:10:32.880 --> 00:10:35.629
Lord told me there are very sobering days

00:10:35.639 --> 00:10:38.590
ahead.

00:10:41.040 --> 00:10:43.710
How the body of Christ

00:10:43.720 --> 00:10:45.829
will get through this is by being

00:10:45.839 --> 00:10:48.550
filled

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:01.629
with the Holy Spirit. In these last

00:11:01.639 --> 00:11:04.310
days, you will have to maintain a spirit

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:08.430
of joy and

00:11:11.509 --> 00:11:11.519
keep

00:11:14.040 --> 00:11:16.389
yourself under the umbrella of His

00:11:16.399 --> 00:11:18.750
protection,

00:11:23.639 --> 00:11:26.590
understanding your

00:11:26.600 --> 00:11:29.430
covenant and

00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:31.710
walking in your authority in

00:11:31.710 --> 00:11:31.720
Psalm

00:11:31.720 --> 00:11:34.829
91 and Psalm 23.

00:11:51.320 --> 00:11:54.310
I believe with all my heart we will

00:11:54.320 --> 00:11:57.430
see the plague; it will come

00:11:57.440 --> 00:11:59.949
and

00:11:59.959 --> 00:12:02.190
do what the Bible said: plagues and pestilences. Do we fear it?

00:12:02.200 --> 00:12:04.590
No,

00:12:04.600 --> 00:12:07.430
but

00:12:07.440 --> 00:12:11.629
we

00:12:11.639 --> 00:12:13.790
are

00:12:13.800 --> 00:12:15.550
here

00:12:15.560 --> 00:12:17.629
for the birthing pains.

00:12:19.519 --> 00:12:22.710
As labor pains upon a woman,

00:12:22.720 --> 00:12:24.509
they get more intense.

00:12:29.639 --> 00:12:33.470
He said He would

00:12:33.480 --> 00:12:35.269
always provide for and take care of His beloved.

00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:46.870
We walk with wisdom

00:12:46.870 --> 00:12:46.880
and

00:12:46.880 --> 00:12:49.829
pray

00:12:49.839 --> 00:12:52.189
over what He tells us.

00:12:54.360 --> 00:12:56.829
The body of Christ must rise up

00:12:56.839 --> 00:12:59.670
more than ever and take

00:12:59.670 --> 00:12:59.680
authority

00:12:59.680 --> 00:13:01.990
so that the devil

00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:03.670
does not get a foothold.

00:13:03.680 --> 00:13:06.829
The Lord told me, "When

00:13:06.839 --> 00:13:08.829
the election's over is not when

00:13:08.839 --> 00:13:11.750
this starts; it's when you put your

00:13:11.760 --> 00:13:14.629
foot on the gas even harder,

00:13:16.839 --> 00:13:19.670
interceding for what's

00:13:19.670 --> 00:13:19.680
coming."The

00:13:19.680 --> 00:13:21.829
enemy

00:13:21.839 --> 00:13:26.550
has a plan, and we are to put a kink

00:13:26.560 --> 00:13:29.389
in his hose.

00:13:33.720 --> 00:13:36.509
I have a book right here called "The Ultimate Voice"by

00:13:36.509 --> 00:13:36.519
Oral Roberts. Diana is

00:13:36.519 --> 00:13:39.949
reading

00:13:39.959 --> 00:13:41.790
with me

00:13:41.800 --> 00:13:45.470
now. She's

00:13:45.480 --> 00:13:46.949
been helping me

00:13:46.959 --> 00:13:49.069
answer emails; it's been

00:13:49.079 --> 00:13:51.030
crazy, hasn't it, babe?

00:13:51.040 --> 00:13:52.710
This

00:13:52.710 --> 00:13:52.720
was

00:13:54.949 --> 00:13:54.959
the

00:13:54.959 --> 00:13:57.430
last

00:13:57.440 --> 00:13:59.590
book

00:13:59.600 --> 00:14:02.949
Oral Roberts

00:14:12.199 --> 00:14:15.150
ever wrote

00:14:15.160 --> 00:14:18.189
in his 90s,

00:14:18.189 --> 00:14:18.199
and

00:14:18.199 --> 00:14:21.230
there

00:14:21.230 --> 00:14:21.240
are

00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:23.790
nuggets

00:14:23.800 --> 00:14:26.189
in here on how to

00:14:26.199 --> 00:14:28.470
hear the voice of the Lord for yourself.

00:14:28.480 --> 00:14:30.310
You don't need a prophet to hear

00:14:30.310 --> 00:14:30.320
about

00:14:30.320 --> 00:14:32.710
investments or

00:14:32.720 --> 00:14:34.470
where you're supposed to

00:14:34.480 --> 00:14:37.790
live. You have the Holy

00:14:37.800 --> 00:14:41.110
Spirit inside

00:14:44.759 --> 00:14:47.470
you. Reading books like this fans the

00:14:47.480 --> 00:14:49.710
flame. Diana, read that passage.

00:14:54.110 --> 00:14:54.120
[Diana

00:14:58.240 --> 00:15:00.230
reads]:

00:15:04.199 --> 00:15:06.670
"God will call you to

00:15:06.680 --> 00:15:09.110
become an extension to others of what

00:15:09.120 --> 00:15:11.629
He has done in your life. The area of

00:15:11.639 --> 00:15:14.189
your life that God heals

00:15:14.199 --> 00:15:16.670
is very likely the area of service

00:15:16.670 --> 00:15:16.680
He

00:15:16.680 --> 00:15:19.470
wants you to extend to others.

00:15:19.480 --> 00:15:21.990
The

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:23.910
person who has been healed emotionally

00:15:23.920 --> 00:15:26.509
from abuse becomes a healer to those who

00:15:26.519 --> 00:15:28.710
are abused. The person who has been

00:15:28.720 --> 00:15:30.790
healed physically becomes a nurse

00:15:30.800 --> 00:15:33.710
or physician.

00:15:52.360 --> 00:15:55.670
No person

00:15:55.680 --> 00:15:57.910
can minister God’s love to another

00:15:57.920 --> 00:16:00.590
person beyond his level of personal

00:16:00.600 --> 00:16:03.590
experience. To

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:05.710
minister

00:16:05.710 --> 00:16:05.720
God’s

00:16:05.720 --> 00:16:08.509
love,

00:16:08.519 --> 00:16:10.990
the other person must know that you have

00:16:11.000 --> 00:16:13.749
been where he is.

00:16:18.360 --> 00:16:21.189
You will find it difficult to

00:16:21.199 --> 00:16:23.509
believe for others to have a miracle

00:16:23.519 --> 00:16:26.350
unless you have

00:16:26.360 --> 00:16:28.269
experienced that miracle in your own

