00:37:00.560 --> 00:37:03.270
Abraham.

00:37:03.280 --> 00:37:05.990
We walk in divine health in a

00:37:06.000 --> 00:37:07.750
greater capacity because we have a

00:37:07.760 --> 00:37:10.230
greater covenant.

00:37:10.230 --> 00:37:10.240
We

00:37:10.240 --> 00:37:13.109
are

00:37:13.119 --> 00:37:15.910
healed by Your stripes.

00:37:15.920 --> 00:37:18.510
If there is any sick among you, call

00:37:18.520 --> 00:37:20.470
for the elders. Back then, it

00:37:20.470 --> 00:37:20.480
was an "if"because

00:37:20.480 --> 00:37:22.109
they weren't

00:37:22.119 --> 00:37:23.630
expecting them to

00:37:23.640 --> 00:37:26.870
be

00:37:26.880 --> 00:37:29.470
sick.

00:37:43.950 --> 00:37:43.960
We

00:37:56.240 --> 00:38:00.190
thank You that we walk in

00:38:00.200 --> 00:38:03.190
Divine Healing.

00:38:19.720 --> 00:38:22.270
We are called to be the

00:38:22.280 --> 00:38:24.349
salt of the earth.

00:38:28.240 --> 00:38:30.910
As we draw nigh to You, You draw

00:38:30.920 --> 00:38:35.030
nigh to us. We seek

00:38:46.520 --> 00:38:49.710
Your face

00:38:49.720 --> 00:38:53.910
every day because

00:38:53.920 --> 00:38:56.589
we're desperate for Your voice

00:38:56.589 --> 00:38:56.599
and

00:38:56.599 --> 00:38:59.030
an

00:38:59.040 --> 00:39:02.870
intimate relationship.

00:39:02.870 --> 00:39:02.880
We

00:39:02.880 --> 00:39:05.190
want to

00:39:05.190 --> 00:39:05.200
follow

00:39:05.200 --> 00:39:07.430
the voice

00:39:07.440 --> 00:39:10.390
of the Lord

00:39:10.390 --> 00:39:10.400
and

00:39:10.400 --> 00:39:13.230
be filled with and controlled by the

00:39:13.240 --> 00:39:16.190
Holy Spirit.

00:39:16.200 --> 00:39:19.470
Holy Spirit, we thank You that You

00:39:19.480 --> 00:39:22.630
are a great comforter and teacher.

00:39:22.630 --> 00:39:22.640
We

00:39:24.950 --> 00:39:24.960
hear

00:39:24.960 --> 00:39:27.470
Your

00:39:27.480 --> 00:39:30.630
voice

00:39:33.599 --> 00:39:37.069
all the

00:39:37.079 --> 00:39:40.470
time. I am good at hearing

00:39:40.480 --> 00:39:41.870
the voice of the

00:39:41.880 --> 00:39:44.670
Lord.

00:39:44.670 --> 00:39:44.680
He

00:39:44.680 --> 00:39:49.550
is

00:39:49.560 --> 00:39:52.589
speaking to me

00:39:52.599 --> 00:39:55.390
now.

00:39:57.440 --> 00:40:00.270
We

00:40:06.069 --> 00:40:06.079
have

00:40:14.109 --> 00:40:14.119
an

00:40:20.599 --> 00:40:22.190
inward

00:40:22.200 --> 00:40:25.589
knowing;

00:40:25.599 --> 00:40:27.710
no confusion with

00:40:27.710 --> 00:40:27.720
a

00:40:27.720 --> 00:40:29.589
demonic spirit.

00:40:37.319 --> 00:40:40.710
We take authority over the spirit

00:40:40.720 --> 00:40:43.829
of torment and fear.

00:40:55.160 --> 00:40:59.190
We hear clearly

00:40:59.200 --> 00:41:01.270
what the Father has to say.

00:41:08.800 --> 00:41:10.910
This is

00:41:10.920 --> 00:41:13.030
the day the Lord has made; we will

00:41:13.040 --> 00:41:15.710
rejoice and be glad in it. We're so

00:41:15.720 --> 00:41:17.829
thankful that

00:41:17.839 --> 00:41:19.990
we have another day to do

00:41:20.000 --> 00:41:22.510
something big for You.

00:41:22.520 --> 00:41:25.589
Amen. Well, we

00:41:25.599 --> 00:41:28.069
believe that for you today.

00:41:28.079 --> 00:41:30.349
This is a time like no

00:41:30.359 --> 00:41:33.910
other. That fly—I hate those

00:41:33.920 --> 00:41:37.390
flies—is

00:41:37.400 --> 00:41:38.910
trying to distract while

00:41:38.920 --> 00:41:41.030
we're praying.

00:41:42.240 --> 00:41:44.990
You better count your

00:41:45.000 --> 00:41:48.069
seconds, buddy; you're fixing to

00:41:48.069 --> 00:41:48.079
be

00:41:48.079 --> 00:41:51.109
gone.

00:42:05.079 --> 00:42:07.309
People probably pointed him out in the

00:42:07.319 --> 00:42:08.750
comments.

00:42:11.119 --> 00:42:13.710
We're excited you're here

00:42:13.720 --> 00:42:16.470
today. Like

00:42:16.480 --> 00:42:19.230
the video and subscribe.

00:42:21.599 --> 00:42:24.670
Click the notification

00:42:24.680 --> 00:42:30.270
