00:42:39.839 --> 00:42:41.470
throughout the whole world.

00:42:54.760 --> 00:42:56.430
If you're

00:42:56.440 --> 00:42:58.870
interested

00:42:58.880 --> 00:43:00.630
in the book,

00:43:00.640 --> 00:43:03.430
