00:43:33.119 --> 00:43:34.390
Thank you for

00:43:34.400 --> 00:43:36.910
joining us today. We will be here

00:43:36.920 --> 00:43:40.589
again tomorrow.

00:43:40.589 --> 00:43:40.599
I

00:43:40.599 --> 00:43:42.030
believe

00:43:42.040 --> 00:43:45.670
this is day 40.

00:43:51.640 --> 00:43:54.109
I feel like the Lord told me to do

00:43:54.119 --> 00:43:55.910
this full-time. Prayer

00:43:55.910 --> 00:43:55.920
changes things;

00:43:55.920 --> 00:43:59.510
it's

00:43:59.510 --> 00:43:59.520
the

00:43:59.520 --> 00:44:02.710
only

00:44:02.720 --> 00:44:04.990
thing

00:44:04.990 --> 00:44:05.000
that

00:44:05.000 --> 00:44:08.950
does.

00:44:08.960 --> 00:44:11.390
I

00:44:11.400 --> 00:44:14.069
appreciate your prayers because when

00:44:14.079 --> 00:44:17.190
you

00:44:17.200 --> 00:44:20.589
disrupt

00:44:20.599 --> 00:44:22.670
the kingdom of

00:44:22.680 --> 00:44:25.150
darkness, they don't like that.

00:44:30.549 --> 00:44:30.559
Diana

00:44:35.839 --> 00:44:39.670
and

00:44:46.309 --> 00:44:46.319
I

00:44:51.559 --> 00:44:53.549
